			</p>
			<div class="flex justify-start items-center gap-x-4 mt-8">
    <a href="https://x.com/sam__brd" target="_blank" class="rounded-xl bg-white p-1.5 size-12 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110 hover:rotate-3">
					<Image class="h-full w-full rounded-lg object-cover" src={twitter} alt="x" />
				</a>
				<a href="https://github.com/barraudSamuel" target="_blank" class="rounded-xl bg-white p-1.5 size-12 transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-110 hover:rotate-3">
